Description
Use the provided legacy code and optimize it to improve code quality and/or performance. This challenge will help you practice code optimization and refactoring.

Expectation:

Analyze the provided legacy code.

Identify areas for improvement in terms of code quality and performance.

Refactor the code to optimize it while maintaining its original functionality.

Ensure the optimized code is well-documented and includes comments explaining the changes made.